service.name: Run That Town
service.description: Lets you play an interactive strategy game with real census data. It puts you in charge of any Australian neighbourhood and challenges you to develop the area and make decisions that will sway popular opinion in your favour.

Dimension.name: Australian Bureau of Statistics
Dimension.desc: The Australian Bureau of Statistics (ABS) is the statistical agency of the Government of Australia. The ABS provides key statistics on a wide range of economic, environmental and social issues, to assist and encourage informed decision making, research and discussion within governments and the community. (source: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Australian_Bureau_of_Statistics)
